 href="https://www.nme.com/artists/london-grammar">伦敦语法</a>。我去参加了雷丁节，那是你四处走走的时刻之一，这就是我喜欢节日的原因，当你四处走动时，你会说，“听起来不错”，进来吧。然后你就可以了。就像，“哇，我最喜欢的新乐队”，那就是伦敦文法学校。是的，很特别。”</p><p> <em>《最后的晚宴》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-autumn-2024-european-tour-3755882">将于今年秋季开始欧洲巡回演唱会</a>。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-last-dinner-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F5395177" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取门票和更多信息。</em> </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-interview-mercury-prize-silence-is-loud-reading-leeds-chevron-beyonce-3779711"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p><em>雷丁和利兹大学将于八月银行假日周末回归。两个地点的门票现已发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Freading-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F12885" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处（雷丁）</a>和<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fleeds-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F35438" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处（利兹）</a>购买。</em></p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-interview-lollapalooza-new-album-mercury-prize-reading-leeds-3781168">《最后的晚宴》一文告诉我们他们的“蒸汽朋克”下一张专辑以及 Reading &amp; Leeds 的计划</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
